      "id": 5,
      "title": "⚙️ Layer 7 — Node.js Runtime",
      "type": "row",
      "panels": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "fieldConfig": {
            "defaults": {
              "unit": "bytes",
              "color": {
                "mode": "palette-classic"
              },
              "custom": {
                "lineWidth": 2,
                "fillOpacity": 10,
                "gradientMode": "opacity",
                "showPoints": "never"
              }
            },
            "overrides": [
              {
                "matcher": {
                  "id": "byName",
                  "options": "Heap Total"
                },
                "properties": [
                  {
                    "id": "custom.lineStyle",
                    "value": {
                      "fill": "dash",
                      "dash": [
                        10,
                        10
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          "gridPos": {
            "h": 8,
            "w": 12,
            "x": 0,
            "y": 43
          },
          "id": 50,
          "options": {
            "tooltip": {
              "mode": "multi",
              "sort": "desc"
            },
            "legend": {
              "displayMode": "list",
              "placement": "bottom"
            }
          },
          "targets": [
            {
              "datasource": {
                "type": "prometheus",
                "uid": "prometheus"
              },
              "expr": "nodejs_heap_size_used_bytes{job=\"authapi\"}",
              "legendFormat": "Heap Used",
              "refId": "A"
            },
            {
              "datasource": {
                "type": "prometheus",
                "uid": "prometheus"
              },
              "expr": "nodejs_heap_size_total_bytes{job=\"authapi\"}",
              "legendFormat": "Heap Total",
              "refId": "B"
            },
            {
              "datasource": {
                "type": "prometheus",
                "uid": "prometheus"
              },
              "expr": "nodejs_external_memory_bytes{job=\"authapi\"}",
              "legendFormat": "External Memory",
              "refId": "C"
            }
          ],
          "title": "Heap Memory — Used / Total / External",
          "type": "timeseries",
          "description": "**What it measures:** V8 heap memory allocation.\n\n**Heap Used:** Active JS objects. Watch for monotonic growth (memory leak).\n**Heap Total:** Memory allocated by V8. Grows in chunks.\n**External:** C++ objects bound to JS (Buffers, etc.).\n\nIf Heap Used approaches Heap Total consistently, the GC is under pressure.",
          "interval": "1m"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "fieldConfig": {
            "defaults": {
              "unit": "s",
              "color": {
                "mode": "palette-classic"
              },
              "custom": {
                "lineWidth": 2,
                "fillOpacity": 10,
                "gradientMode": "opacity",
                "showPoints": "never"
              },
              "thresholds": {
                "mode": "absolute",
                "steps": [
                  {
                    "color": "green",
                    "value": null
                  },
                  {
                    "color": "yellow",
                    "value": 0.05
                  },
                  {
                    "color": "red",
                    "value": 0.1
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "overrides": [
              {
                "matcher": {
                  "id": "byName",
                  "options": "p99 lag"
                },
                "properties": [
                  {
                    "id": "color",
                    "value": {
                      "mode": "fixed",
                      "fixedColor": "red"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          "gridPos": {
            "h": 8,
            "w": 12,
            "x": 12,
            "y": 43
          },
          "id": 51,
          "options": {
            "tooltip": {
              "mode": "multi",
              "sort": "desc"
            },
            "legend": {
              "displayMode": "list",
              "placement": "bottom"
            }
          },
          "targets": [
            {
              "datasource": {
                "type": "prometheus",
                "uid": "prometheus"
              },
              "expr": "nodejs_eventloop_lag_p50_seconds{job=\"authapi\"}",
              "legendFormat": "p50 lag",
              "refId": "A"
            },
            {
              "datasource": {
                "type": "prometheus",
                "uid": "prometheus"
              },
              "expr": "nodejs_eventloop_lag_p99_seconds{job=\"authapi\"}",
              "legendFormat": "p99 lag",
              "refId": "B"
            },
            {
              "datasource": {
                "type": "prometheus",
                "uid": "prometheus"
              },
              "expr": "nodejs_eventloop_lag_seconds{job=\"authapi\"}",
              "legendFormat": "Current lag",
              "refId": "C"
            }
          ],
          "title": "Event Loop Lag — p50 / p99 / Current",
          "type": "timeseries",
          "description": "**What it measures:** How long callbacks wait before the event loop picks them up.\n\n**Healthy:** <10ms p99. **Warning:** >50ms (CPU-bound work or heavy sync I/O blocking the loop).\n**Critical:** >100ms — the Node.js process is saturated.\n\nCorrelate spikes with GC pauses (major GC) or CPU usage.",
          "interval": "1m"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "fieldConfig": {
            "defaults": {
              "unit": "s",
              "color": {
                "mode": "palette-classic"
              },
              "custom": {
                "lineWidth": 2,
                "fillOpacity": 15,
                "gradientMode": "opacity",
                "showPoints": "never",
                "stacking": {
                  "mode": "normal"
                }
              }
            },
            "overrides": [
              {
                "matcher": {
                  "id": "byRegexp",
                  "options": ".*major.*"
                },
                "properties": [
                  {
                    "id": "color",
                    "value": {
                      "mode": "fixed",
                      "fixedColor": "red"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "matcher": {
                  "id": "byRegexp",
                  "options": ".*minor.*"
                },
                "properties": [
                  {
                    "id": "color",
                    "value": {
                      "mode": "fixed",
                      "fixedColor": "green"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "matcher": {
                  "id": "byRegexp",
                  "options": ".*incremental.*"
                },
                "properties": [
                  {
                    "id": "color",
                    "value": {
                      "mode": "fixed",
                      "fixedColor": "yellow"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          "gridPos": {
            "h": 8,
            "w": 12,
            "x": 0,
            "y": 51
          },
          "id": 52,
          "options": {
            "tooltip": {
              "mode": "multi",
              "sort": "desc"
            },
